						<p>It records the restoration of <hi rend="italic">aḷḷu</hi> remittance (a handful of grain as tax) from the Friday fair held at this village, to the temple of Tiruvirāmayar by one Ādichchadēvamudaliār and Enthiyānāyakkar.</p>						

